{"title":"万首诗歌写满墙——中国文联参观团题在河北省怀来县花园乡的街头诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"万首诗歌写满墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——中国文联参观团题在河北省怀来县花园乡的街头诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡是花果乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡是诗歌乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万株果树种满园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万首诗歌写满墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花秆子成塔尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空酒瓶制水平仪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅学习个把月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满乡都是技术师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五个电力扬水站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一季工夫抵四年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少齐出力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡变小江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往前赶，努力钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶到“七一”把礼献；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革命已开端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过英国并不难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年5月24日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡是大花园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡是大花园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南水泉是珍珠泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前是荒山和沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在是花果山、米粮川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南面栽起防风林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北面修成扬水站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村社墙头满诗画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫厅湖上走渔船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义农村乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声直上九霄天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进跃进再跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一天等于二十年”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访花园乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶圣陶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来访已过花时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却见此乡到处花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲远景说不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心上开红花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭老题诗说得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡是诗歌乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真诗原从生活出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进时诗满墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间  马秉顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭老题诗在街头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泉诗歌遍地游；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗歌游到官厅湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐上一条大木船；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘东风，争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年胜过十八秋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员都是好歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食诗歌双丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎参观团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀来县委副书记  王俊禄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南水泉花果满园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来北京参观团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文艺星斗光芒四射，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡成了百花园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭老月下留诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞我们大生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人画家齐挥笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗歌万首画一千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花园乡里南水泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术家种了试验田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们欢迎参观团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用空话用实干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心书一篇又一篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心要赶到长江边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的雄心大如山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘掉帽子敢碰天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑上快马再加鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年计划五年完。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}